===望月新一===
2012年5月，计算机科学家[[泰德·尼爾森|泰德·尼爾森]]认为中本聰就是日本数学家[[望月新一|望月新一]]，认为其足够聪明，研究领域包含比特币所使用的数学算法。更重要的是，望月不使用常规的学术发表机制，而是习惯是独自工作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=emDJTGTrEm0 |title=I Think I Know Who Satoshi Is - YouTube |accessdate=2014-03-18 |archive-date=2014-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414151824/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=emDJTGTrEm0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而也有人提出质疑，认为设计比特币所需的[[密码学|密码学]]并非望月的研究兴趣。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/timworstall/2013/05/19/ted-nelson-says-that-bitcons-satoshi-nakamoto-is-shinichi-mochizuki/|author=Tim Worstall|title=Ted Nelson Says That Bitcoin's Satoshi Nakamoto Is Shinichi Mochizuki|date=2013-05-19|publisher=Forbes|accessdate=2013-09-04|archive-date=2013-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130831223329/http://www.forbes.com/sites/timworstall/2013/05/19/ted-nelson-says-that-bitcons-satoshi-nakamoto-is-shinichi-mochizuki/|dead-url=no}}</ref>望月本人亦予以否认。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.theage.com.au/technology/technology-news/the-outlaw-cult-20130709-2po5j.html|publisher=The Age|date=2013-07-10|title=The outlaw cult|author=Eileen Ormsby|accessdate=2013-09-04|archive-date=2013-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122125718/http://www.theage.com.au/technology/technology-news/the-outlaw-cult-20130709-2po5j.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===尼克·薩博===
2013年12月，博客作家Skye Grey通过对中本论文的{{link-en|计量文体学|Stylometry}}分析得出结论，认为其真实身份是前[[乔治华盛顿大学|乔治华盛顿大学]]教授[[尼克·薩博|尼克·薩博]]。薩博热衷于去中心化货币，还发表过一篇关于“比特黄金”（bit gold）的论文，被认为是比特币的先驱。<ref>{{cite news |author=John Biggs |url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/12/05/who-is-the-real-satoshi-nakamoto-one-researcher-may-have-found-the-answer/ |title=Who is the real Satoshi Nakamoto? One researcher may have found the answer |publisher=TechCrunch |date= |accessdate=2014-03-06 |archive-date=2014-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313180301/http://techcrunch.com/2013/12/05/who-is-the-real-satoshi-nakamoto-one-researcher-may-have-found-the-answer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Grey, Skye |url=https://likeinamirror.wordpress.com/2013/12/01/satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-nick-szabo/ |title=Satoshi Nakamoto is (probably) Nick Szabo |date=2013-12-01 |accessdate=2014-03-13 |archive-date=2016-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503070538/https://likeinamirror.wordpress.com/2013/12/01/satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-nick-szabo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Grey, Skye |url=https://likeinamirror.wordpress.com/2014/03/11/occams-razor-who-is-most-likely-to-be-satoshi-nakamoto/ |title=Occam’s Razor: who is most likely to be Satoshi Nakamoto? |date=2014-03-11 |accessdate=2014-03-15 |archive-date=2014-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314145252/http://likeinamirror.wordpress.com/2014/03/11/occams-razor-who-is-most-likely-to-be-satoshi-nakamoto/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他也是一个著名的从90年代起就喜欢使用[[化名|化名]]的人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cypherpunks.venona.com/date/1993/10/msg00759.html |title=Re: on anonymity, identity, reputation, and spoofing |date=1993-10-18 |accessdate=2014-03-15 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316020636/http://cypherpunks.venona.com/date/1993/10/msg00759.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2011年5月的一篇文章中，薩博谈起比特币创造者时表示：“在我认识的人里面，对这个想法足够感兴趣，并且能付诸实施的，本来只有我自己、{{tsl|en|Wei Dai|戴维 (计算机科学家)|戴维}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lesswrong.com/lw/jgz/aalwa_ask_any_lesswronger_anything/apj0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-03-06 |archive-date=2016-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021180117/http://lesswrong.com/lw/jgz/aalwa_ask_any_lesswronger_anything/apj0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[哈爾·芬尼|哈爾·芬尼]]三个人，后来中本出现了（假定中本不是芬尼也不是戴維）。”<ref>{{cite news |author=Nick Szabo |url=http://unenumerated.blogspot.com/2011/05/bitcoin-what-took-ye-so-long.html |title=Bitcoin, what took ye so long? |date=2011-05-28 |accessdate=2014-03-12 |archive-date=2014-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217103323/http://unenumerated.blogspot.com/2011/05/bitcoin-what-took-ye-so-long.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===多利安·中本===
最为公众所熟知的猜测发生在2014年3月6日。[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]记者{{link-en|Leah McGrath Goodman|Leah McGrath Goodman}}发表文章称自己已经找到真正的中本，是一个居住在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[日裔美国人|日裔美国人]]，名叫'''多利安·中本'''，而其[[和名|和名]]正正就是中本哲史。<ref name="newsweek">{{cite magazine | url=http://mag.newsweek.com/2014/03/14/bitcoin-satoshi-nakamoto.html | title=The Face Behind Bitcoin | work=Newsweek | date=6 March 2014 | accessdate=6 March 2014 | author=Leah McGrath Goodman | archive-date=2014-03-07 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6NtE8qHbJ?url=http://mag.newsweek.com/2014/03/14/bitcoin-satoshi-nakamoto.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>除了名字相同以外，Goodman还找到了一些佐证，其中最有力的一条是，当Goodman在当面采访并提出比特币的问题时，多利安的回答看起来确认了其比特币之父的身份：“我已经不再参与它了，不能讨论它。它已经被转交给其他人。他们现在在负责。我已经没有任何联系。”<ref name="newsweek" />这段话的真实性亦得到了当时在场的[[洛杉矶郡|洛杉矶郡]][[警察|警察]]的确认。<ref>{{cite news | first = Richard | last = Winton | title = Deputies: Newsweek Bitcoin story quoted Satoshi Nakamoto accurately | date = 2014-03-07 | url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-la-sheriffs-say-satoshi-nakamoto-man-did-talk-about-bitcoin-to-newsweek-reporter-20140307,0,609860.story | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-03-09 | archive-date = 2014-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308181437/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-la-sheriffs-say-satoshi-nakamoto-man-did-talk-about-bitcoin-to-newsweek-reporter-20140307,0,609860.story | dead-url = no }}</ref>

报道被公开后受到了包括比特币社区在内舆论的质疑和批评<ref>{{cite news |author=Andy Greenberg |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/andygreenberg/2014/03/06/bitcoin-community-responds-to-satoshi-nakamotos-outing-with-disbelief-anger-fascination/ |title=Bitcoin Community Responds To Satoshi Nakamoto's Outing With Disbelief, Anger, Fascination |publisher=Forbes |date= |accessdate=2014-03-06 |archive-date=2014-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307190253/http://www.forbes.com/sites/andygreenberg/2014/03/06/bitcoin-community-responds-to-satoshi-nakamotos-outing-with-disbelief-anger-fascination/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但同时也引起了媒体的巨大兴趣。记者们蜂拥而至多利安的住宅外蹲守，甚至追逐他的汽车。<ref name="latimes dorian denial">{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-bitcoin-founder-la-chased-20140306,0,3692933.story |title=Dorian Satoshi Nakamoto chased by reporters, denies founding Bitcoin |first=Salvador |last=Rodriguez |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2014-03-06 |accessdate=2014-03-06 |archive-date=2014-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306233446/http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-bitcoin-founder-la-chased-20140306,0,3692933.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而在后来的正式访谈中，多利安否认了自己与比特币的全部联系，称自己从未听说过，只是误解了Goodman的提问，以为她问的是自己之前从军方承接的保密性工作。<ref name="Nakashima">{{cite web |last=Nakashima |first=Ryan |url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_BITCOIN_FOUNDER_DENIAL?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2014-03-06-19-35-06 |title=Man said to create Bitcoin denies it |publisher=Hosted.ap.org |accessdate=2014-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307065618/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_BITCOIN_FOUNDER_DENIAL?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2014-03-06-19-35-06 |archivedate=2014-03-07 }}</ref>

当天晚些时候，中本聰本人也站出来否认。他在P2P基金会的账户在尘封五年之后发了第一条消息，称：“我不是多利安·中本。”<ref name="p2p_foundation">{{cite web |url=http://p2pfoundation.ning.com/forum/topics/bitcoin-open-source?commentId=2003008%3AComment%3A52186 |title=Bitcoin open source implementation of P2P currency |date=2014-03-07 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archive-date=2014-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307021221/http://p2pfoundation.ning.com/forum/topics/bitcoin-open-source%3FcommentId=2003008%253AComment%253A52186 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=加洲男子否認是比特幣發明者中本聰 遭媒體包圍飛車追逐 |url=http://technews.tw/2014/03/07/the-man-denied-he-is-bitcoin-inventer-surround-by-media/ |author=infortron |date=2014-03-07 |accessdate=2014-03-10 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2014-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310185136/http://technews.tw/2014/03/07/the-man-denied-he-is-bitcoin-inventer-surround-by-media/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 克雷格·史蒂芬·怀特 ===
2015年12月，《连线杂志》报道说[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]学者[[克雷格·史蒂芬·怀特|克雷格·史蒂芬·怀特]]很有可能是中本聪的[[本尊|本尊]]。同时也指出，也许只是他精心设计的一个高明的骗局想让我们相信他就是中本聪本人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/12/bitcoins-creator-satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-this-unknown-australian-genius/|title=Bitcoin's Creator Satoshi Nakamoto Is Probably This Unknown Australian Genius|accessdate=2015-12-10|archive-date=2015-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210025320/http://www.wired.com/2015/12/bitcoins-creator-satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-this-unknown-australian-genius/|dead-url=no}}</ref>直到2016年5月2日，[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]企業家克雷格·史蒂芬·懷特公開承認自己就是發明比特幣的中本聰，首度有人公開承認。其證據是中本聪的加密簽名檔，但被質疑該檔只要是稍微高階一點的[[駭客|駭客]]都能在[[暗網|暗網]]中找到下載<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/105769 |title=疑雲未解 |accessdate=2016-05-14 |archive-date=2016-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514035637/http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/105769 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，早就在不少電腦高手圈流傳，另一證據是早期第1及第9區塊比特幣位址的私鑰，但此私鑰如果是早期比特幣開發人員或其親近者都有可能拿到。

最關鍵證明是匯入比特幣至2009年的比特幣第一筆交易地址，該地址被視為是中本聰所有，並要求表演匯回，BBC記者將0.017個比特幣匯入，但最終沒有匯回。BBC刊登-{}-出和他的訪談片段，自稱他就是比特币发明者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-36168863|title=Creator of Bitcoin digital cash reveals identity|accessdate=2 May 2016|date=2 May 2016|publisher=BBC|website=BBC News|archive-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107035542/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-36168863|dead-url=no}}</ref>但克雷格聲明與證據的真實性受到普遍的質疑，在最後階段要求演示關鍵證據時，克雷格拒絕並發佈了一篇顧左右而言他的博客文章<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/05/160502_bitcoins_inventor|title=比特幣發明者克雷格·賴特公開自己身份|accessdate=2016-05-02|date=2016-05-02|publisher=bbc.com|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503111859/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/05/160502_bitcoins_inventor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Vincent van Volkmer ===
自2018年以來，互聯網聲稱美國藝術家Vincent van Volkmer是中本聰。對此同時也有一系列證據，例如：他談到他是一名數學家和密碼學家的事實，他也與擁有導致阻礙技術相關知識的專家保持著良好的聯繫。不過，他自己也反駁了他就是中本聰的這種說法。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Is Vincent van Volkmer the bitcoin developer and inventor Satoshi Nakamoto? – CryptoNews – Cryptocurrency news, bitcoin, ethereum, blockchain, smart contracts|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/comments/aczea0/is_vincent_van_volkmer_the_bitcoin_developer_and/|accessdate=2019-02-09|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220203904/https://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/comments/aczea0/is_vincent_van_volkmer_the_bitcoin_developer_and/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Vincent van Volkmer artist - biography|url=https://www.vincentvanvolkmer.com/Vincent-van-Volkmer-ENG|work=www.vincentvanvolkmer.com|accessdate=2019-02-09|language=de|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209180549/https://www.vincentvanvolkmer.com/Vincent-van-Volkmer-ENG|archive-date=2019-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Vincent van Volkmer is not the bitcoin inventor and developer Satoshi Nakamoto|url=https://www.vincentvanvolkmer.com/Satoshi-Nakamoto-ENG|work=www.vincentvanvolkmer.com|accessdate=2019-02-09|language=de|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117013309/https://www.vincentvanvolkmer.com/Satoshi-Nakamoto-ENG|archive-date=2019-01-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 金子勇 ===
區塊鏈的專家{{Link-ja|仲津正朗|仲津正朗}}提出了日籍程式設計師、檔案共享軟體[[Winny|Winny]]開發者[[金子勇|金子勇]]即是中本聰的假說，該假說於2019年開始在網上流傳。作為根據，仲津提到了與金子有過交流的技術人員的理論間的關聯性，P2P技術構造上的共通性，以及論文中透露出的“對既存系統的不信任感”（仲津認為由於{{Link-ja|Winny事件|Winny事件}}而被國家浪費了才能和時間的金子本人亦有相同感受）。除此之外，中本聰從未使用其所持有的100萬比特幣以及從不暴露真實身份的特徵，都可以由金子勇本人已經死亡這一事實來說明。<ref>{{Cite web|title=「サトシ」はあの日本人？ 仮想通貨生んだ天才を追った|url=https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN394S5VN2JULFA00C.html|access-date=2021-08-21|archive-date=2021-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210821105737/https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN394S5VN2JULFA00C.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===其它猜测===
还有一些其他个人或团体被认为是中本聰的真身。其中包括：
* 芬兰经济社会学家Dr Vili Lehdonvirta及爱尔兰密码学研究生Michael Clear。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2011/10/10/111010fa_fact_davis?currentPage=all | title=The Crypto-Currency | work=The New Yorker | date=10 October 2011 | accessdate=17 December 2013 | author=Davis, Joshua | archive-date=2013-12-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217120451/http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2011/10/10/111010fa_fact_davis?currentPage=all | dead-url=no }}</ref>两人分别否认。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.scss.tcd.ie/~clearm/bitcoin.html | title=Clarifications on Joshua Davis' Article on Bitcoin in the New Yorker | date=4 April 2013 | accessdate=17 December 2013 | author=Clear, Michael | archive-date=2013-10-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031180459/https://www.scss.tcd.ie/~clearm/bitcoin.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="coindesk">{{cite web | url=http://www.coindesk.com/information/who-is-satoshi-nakamoto/ | title=Who is Satoshi Nakamoto? | publisher=coindesk.com | date=26 November 2013 | accessdate=17 December 2013 | archive-date=2013-11-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131125155821/http://www.coindesk.com/information/who-is-satoshi-nakamoto/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 德国及美国研究人员Neal King、Vladimir Oksman和Charles Bry。<ref name="Penenberg">{{cite web | url=http://www.fastcompany.com/1785445/bitcoin-crypto-currency-mystery-reopened | title=The Bitcoin Crypto-currency Mystery Reopened | publisher=The Fast Company | date=11 October 2011 | accessdate=17 December 2013 | author=Penenberg, Adam | archive-date=2013-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006235216/http://www.fastcompany.com/1785445/bitcoin-crypto-currency-mystery-reopened | dead-url=no }}</ref>他们曾共同申请注册一项与比特币相关的专利，而比特币项目官方网站的域名bitcoin.org恰好注册于专利申请提交之后的第三天。<ref>{{US patent|20100042841|Updating and Distributing Encryption Keys US 20100042841 A1}}</ref>三人均否认此猜测。<ref name="Penenberg" />
* 比特币基金会首席科学家{{link-en|Gavin Andresen|Gavin Andresen}}、比特币交易平台[[Mt._Gox|Mt. Gox]]创始人Jed McCaleb，或某个政府机构。<ref name="liu2013" />
* 美国企业家及安全研究员Dustin D. Trammell，但他公开否认。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.dustintrammell.com/2013/11/26/i-am-not-satoshi|title=I am not Satoshi|accessdate=2014-02-21|format=blog|archive-date=2014-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217003002/http://blog.dustintrammell.com/2013/11/26/i-am-not-satoshi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 也有人认为Satoshi Nakamoto的名字实际上是四家公司名字的组合，包括[[三星電子|三星]]（'''Sa'''msung）、[[东芝|东芝]]（'''Toshi'''ba）、[[Nakamichi|中道]]（'''Naka'''michi）和[[摩托罗拉|摩托罗拉]]（'''Moto'''rola），暗示着比特币其实是这四家公司联手开发并以Satoshi Nakamoto，即“中本聰”的化名来发表。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bitcoinexaminer.org/who-is-satoshi-nakamoto|title=Who is Satoshi Nakamoto?|accessdate=2014-03-12|format=blog|publisher=Bitcoin Examiner|archive-date=2014-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313120800/http://bitcoinexaminer.org/who-is-satoshi-nakamoto/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年3月，Quranium Publishing的总监Hamid Rabei在Quranium网站上的一篇文章中指出，有必要审查和分析《时代》杂志首页上的所有头条新闻（于2009年1月3日发布），以破译中本聪的身份和他建立区块链和货币系统的目标。<ref>{{cite web |title=Satoshi Nakamoto missing link between Bitcoin, Salman Rushdie, Israel and UK |url=http://rabei.ir/satoshi-nakamoto-missing-link-between-bitcoin-salman-rushdie-israel-and-uk/ |website=Academy Of Rabei |language=fa-IR |access-date=2021-03-21 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506004632/http://rabei.ir/satoshi-nakamoto-missing-link-between-bitcoin-salman-rushdie-israel-and-uk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

